# odysseus-submodule-symlink-to-gitlink — History

## v2.0.0 (2026-03-29)

**Changed by:** Skill split — BUILD_ROOT and rebase content extracted to separate skills
**Verification:** verified-local

### What changed
- Removed BUILD_ROOT meta-repo justfile pattern (moved to `meta-repo-build-root-pattern`)
- Removed rebase full-file-rewrite conflict strategy (moved to `rebase-full-file-rewrite-conflict`)
- Narrowed scope to symlink→gitlink conversion only
- Added URL casing mismatch as explicit Failed Attempts row
- Updated description to reflect narrowed scope

### Why
Original v1.0.0 combined three independent learnings into one skill. Skills covering unrelated topics
reduce discoverability — someone searching for rebase conflict resolution would not search for
"submodule symlink". Split into three focused skills.

